{
  "stem": "7722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was-- and he built our whole town especially for the sugar factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He built-- he-- he built a whole town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and it so happened-- and it so happened, what I want to just show you what kind of a-- of a human being my father was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- so I told you for the oil-- for the-- for the ordered products, we-- my-- we gave notes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the notes came in, and you had to pay them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you couldn't pay them, so we bankrupt-- we went bankrupt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Poland, it was customary, they settle with you, 30%, 40%, they settled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we-- when we-- when we didn't pay the note, so they came from-- from those oil refineries, where they sell-- they came, and they want to settle with my father for 40%, 50%.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father told them, I never in my life took [CRYING] from nobody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] Do me only one favor-- give me two years to pay up, and I'll pay you with interest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he paid up the whole 100%.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] He didn't want to take money for nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he wants store, and I'm going to get mixed up the same thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I came to the-- to the States, do you know there is a joint.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave-- they put up the-- the-- all DPs-- they-- all the refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't want to take from them $0.05.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I told them with my-- [CRYING] with my 10 fingers, I'm going to earn a living for my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SOBBING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, now in our part of Poland, they didn't send-- not to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They liquidated town-- town after town.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
